title: Sons of Thunder Pro - Get me Ready for Sunday - Piano Lessons
description:
Get Me Ready for Sunday Worship Songs and Hymns is a piano video designed for those who want to take their piano playing to the next level. The video focuses on working with the melody to create a nice mix between the contemporary and traditional sound. This video utilizes new on screen midi technology. It is perfect for the pianist seeking to develop a ear for song interpretation

This video is composed of 7 separate videos.Chapter 1) As The Deer Basic Breakdown Video 2) As the Deer Advanced Chords and Concepts Worship Ending Turnaround Video 3) Anointing Fall on Me Breakdown Video 4) Give Thanks Breakdown Worship Outro Worship Ending Movement Video 5) I Will Trust In the Lord Breakdown Shuffle Contemporary Chords Alternate Ending Video 6) Oh How I Love Jesus Video 7) Approaching the 4 and 5 Tips
